createEventSet

public java.util.Vector<EventSet> createEventSet(java.util.Vector<DocumentSet> ds)
Description copied from class: EventDriver
EventSet creation method for multiple DocumentSets. Creates a vector of EventSets from a Vector of DocumentSets. By default, simply creates one EventSet independently per DocumentSet, but this can be overridden as necessary if Events are not independent (for instance, if we need frequency information across all documents.

createEventSet in class EventDriver
